<h1>Hello <%= @freelancer.name %>,</h1>

  <p>
    You have successfully accepted the task "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>" on Gighive.
  </p>

  <p>
    Here are the task details:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Title:</strong> <%= @task.title %></li>
    <li><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @task.description %></li>
    <li><strong>Budget:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@task.budget, unit: "ZMK", format: "%u%n") %></li>
    <li><strong>Deadline:</strong> <%= @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    Please coordinate with the client and aim to complete the task on or before the deadline.
  </p>

  <p>
    You can view details here:
    <%= link_to 'View Task on Gighive', task_url(@task) %>
  </p>

  <p>
    We wish you a successful collaboration!
  </p>